            "author": "Hottman",
            "date": "2012-11-24T00:57:54+00:00",
            "content": "<div class=\"post entry-content\" itemprop=\"commentText\">\n\t\t\t\t\tBom pessoal segue anexo as referidas \"Moscas\" se alguem tiver em bom estado ou alguma referencia de onde vende agradeço !<br/>\n<br/>\nSENSOR DO NIVEL DE AGUA ( DO RESERVATORIO DO PARABRISA ) ( 90346055 )<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"resized_img\" href=\"http://www.clubecalibra.com.br/forum/uploads/monthly_11_2012/post-10686-1353718123,5146.jpg\" id=\"ipb-attach-url-\" rel=\"lightbox[336853]\" title=\"$(KGrHqIOKp0E1q0356Z)BNb50-I)gw~~_35.jpg - Tamanho: 4,83K, Downloads: 0\"><img alt=\"$(KGrHqIOKp0E1q0356Z)BNb50-I)gw~~_35.jpg\" class=\"bbc_img linked-image\" itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://www.clubecalibra.com.br/forum/uploads/monthly_11_2012/post-10686-1353718123,5146.jpg\"/></a>\n<br/>\n<br/>\nANEL VEDADOR DO SENSOR ( 90276310 )<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"resized_img\" href=\"http://www.clubecalibra.com.br/forum/uploads/monthly_11_2012/post-10686-1353718343,01.jpg\" id=\"ipb-attach-url-18284-0-70006900-1775914371\" rel=\"lightbox[336853]\" title=\"3385_1.jpg - Tamanho: 43,1K, Downloads: 0\"><img alt=\"3385_1.jpg\" class=\"attach\" height=\"380\" id=\"ipb-attach-img-18284-0-70006900-1775914371\" itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://www.clubecalibra.com.br/forum/uploads/monthly_11_2012/post-10686-1353718343,01_thumb.jpg\" style=\"width:640;height:380\" width=\"640\"/></a>\n<br/>\n<br/>\nBASE DA ANTENA DO TETO ( 90355086 )<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"resized_img\" href=\"http://www.clubecalibra.com.br/forum/uploads/monthly_11_2012/post-10686-1353718546,2125.jpg\" id=\"ipb-attach-url-\" rel=\"lightbox[336853]\" title=\"90355086.jpg - Tamanho: 8,84K, Downloads: 0\"><img alt=\"90355086.jpg\" class=\"bbc_img linked-image\" itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://www.clubecalibra.com.br/forum/uploads/monthly_11_2012/post-10686-1353718546,2125.jpg\"/></a>\n<br/>\n</div>"
        },
